column2: create table weblog (--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- --/H normalized web log entry -- describes a web hit ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- --/T See also the WebLogAll view that denomalizes the table. ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- hitID bigint identity (#, #) not # primary key, --/D unique identifier yy smallint not #, --/D year mm tinyint not #, --/D month dd tinyint not #, --/D day (UTC) hh tinyint not #, --/D hour (UTC) mi tinyint not #, --/D minute ss tinyint not #, --/D second theTime dateTime not #, --/D timestamp logID smallint not #, --/D id of server that generated record /R LogSource clientIpID int not #, --/D id of IP address that generated record /R IpMap opID tinyint not #, --/D id of Web Operation: GET, POST, ... /R webOp stemID int not #, --/D id of web command stem e.g. getJpeg.asp? /R WebCommandStem paramsID int not #, --/D id of web command string e.g. ID = # /R WebCommandParams error smallint not #, --/D HTTP status code agentStringID int not #, --/D webAgentString (e.g. Firefox) /R WebAgentString refererID int not #, --/D page that pointed to this page /R WebReferer bytesOut bigint not #, --/D Bytes in request bytesIn int not #, --/D Bytes in reply elapsed int not #, --/D elapsed time in ms (seems to be unreliable) isvisible bit not #, --/D flag says record is public
